content:
Dear Sheffield City Council,
Please provide the following information relating to the local authority's non-residential social care services provision:
1. Non-residential / home care service charges: please provide the rates charged by the authority for the following services, in the financial years 2020-21; 2021-22, 2022-23, and 2023-24:
i. Homecare: please provide the hourly rate and the minimum unit rate, if applicable;
ii. Pendant alarms / Telecare: please provide the rates for all levels of this service;
iii. Day care: transport: please provide the journey rate and the minimum rate, if applicable;
iv. Day care: please provide the daily and the minimum rate, if applicable.
2. Please confirm if your council has agreed to implement a raise in any of these categories of charge from April 2024, and the agreed increase/s.
Yours faithfully,
Helen Rowlands
